---
name: sol-h800-kernel-opt-sol
version: 1
schema: omhflow/v1
models:
  roles:
    coordinator: infini/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    planner: infini/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    implementer: infini/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    repair: infini/gpt-5.5:xhigh
    architect: infini/claude-opus-4-8:high
    planReviewer: infini/claude-opus-4-8:high
    reviewer: infini/claude-opus-4-8:high
    glm: infini/glm-5.2
    deepseek: infini/deepseek-v4-pro
    searchReviewer: infini/gpt-5.5:xhigh
  defaults:
    agent: coordinator
    review: reviewer
  unavailable: fallback-to-parent
checkpoint:
  stopDeadlineMs: 300000
changePolicy:
  agentsCanPropose: true
  humansCanApprove: true
---
# SOL-ExecBench H800 Kernel Optimization

```yaml workflow
stateSchema:
  version: 1
  shape:
    campaign: object
    skills: object
    wiki: object
    protectedFiles: object
    leaderboard: object
    workerPool: object
    lanes: object
    /campaign/pause: object
    /campaign/continue: boolean
    /campaign/forcedTaskDir: string
